        "section_visibility": "always",
        "custom_liquid": "<div class=\"aaw-home-shell\">\n  <section class=\"aaw-home-section dark\" aria-labelledby=\"aaw-home-path-title\">\n    <div class=\"aaw-home-wrap\">\n      <div class=\"aaw-home-section-head\">\n        <div>\n          <p class=\"aaw-home-kicker\">The range</p>\n          <h2 id=\"aaw-home-path-title\">Three ways in.</h2>\n        </div>\n        <p>Universal monitor. Daily driver. Or your ears, scanned and built around.</p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"aaw-home-product-grid\">\n        <a class=\"aaw-home-product-card feature\" href=\"/products/z07-in-ear-monitor\">\n          <img src=\"{{ 'z07-green-faceplate-closeup-black-tray.jpg' | asset_img_url: '900x' }}\" alt=\"Z07 green and black faceplate detail\" width=\"1696\" height=\"2261\" loading=\"lazy\">\n          <div><span>New universal</span><h3><img class=\"aaw-home-z07-card-logo\" src=\"{{ 'z07-logo.svg' | asset_url }}\" alt=\"Z07\" width=\"257\" height=\"102\"><span class=\"visually-hidden\">Z07 flagship in-ear monitor</span></h3><p>The flagship. Hybrid tubeless core, FitMorph shell, designed to be the last universal you need.</p></div>\n        </a>\n        <a class=\"aaw-home-product-card\" href=\"/products/z05-auag-launch-edition\">\n          <img src=\"{{ 'z05-auag-luxury-portrait-hero.png' | asset_img_url: '900x' }}\" alt=\"Z05 AuAg Launch Edition\" width=\"1024\" height=\"1280\" loading=\"lazy\">\n          <div><span>Daily universal</span><h3>Z05 AuAg</h3><p>Dynamic punch and armature detail, with a TwinCore switch to flip between moods. Small enough to live in a pocket.</p></div>\n        </a>\n        <a class=\"aaw-home-product-card\" href=\"/products/aaw-custom-builder\">\n          <img src=\"{{ 'aaw-ins-gallery-custom-2025.webp' | asset_img_url: '900x' }}\" alt=\"AAW custom in-ear monitor with hand-finished shell\" width=\"1440\" height=\"1440\" loading=\"lazy\">\n          <div><span>Custom build</span><h3>Made to your ears</h3><p>Send impressions. Pick the shell, the faceplate, the wood, the inlay. Receive a monitor that nobody else has and nobody else can wear.</p></div>\n        </a>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n</div>",
