    "aaw_home_service_confidence": {
      "type": "custom-liquid",
      "settings": {
        "section_visibility": "always",
        "custom_liquid": "<div class=\"aaw-home-shell\">\n  <section class=\"aaw-home-service-section\" aria-labelledby=\"aaw-home-service-title\">\n    <div class=\"aaw-home-wrap\">\n      <div class=\"aaw-home-section-head\">\n        <div>\n          <p class=\"aaw-home-kicker\">Service</p>\n          <h2 id=\"aaw-home-service-title\">The part that happens after you pay.</h2>\n        </div>\n        <p>A monitor is a long relationship. Here's what that looks like with us.</p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"aaw-home-service-grid\">\n        <article><span>Before</span><h3>Ear impressions and fit</h3><p>What good impressions look like, where to get them done, and what to expect when a custom shell first goes in your ear.</p></article>\n        <article><span>If something's off</span><h3>Refits and warranty</h3><p>Seal not right. Pressure point in a new spot. Something snapped. Send it back and we'll sort it.</p></article>\n        <article><span>Years later</span><h3>Repair and re-shell</h3><p>Cables, sockets, shells. We still service monitors we built ten years ago. Yours will get the same.</p></article>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"aaw-home-actions\"><a class=\"aaw-home-btn\" href=\"/pages/how-to-take-ear-impression\">Impression guide</a><a class=\"aaw-home-btn secondary\" href=\"/pages/warranty-refit\">Warranty &amp; refit</a></div>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n</div>",
